---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="UE5 修仙 RPG - 林寸" description="虚幻引擎5打造的开放世界修仙游戏。">
  <section class="relative py-32 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <a href="/" class="text-gray-500 hover:text-white text-sm transition-colors mb-8 inline-block">← 返回首页</a>
      <div class="mb-12">
        <span class="text-blue-500 text-sm font-medium">游戏开发</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mt-3">UE5 修仙 RPG</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4 text-lg">虚幻引擎5打造的开放世界修仙游戏</p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-8 text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/5">
          <h2 class="text-white text-xl font-bold mb-4">项目简介</h2>
          <p>一个开放世界的修仙 RPG。不用一行 C++，纯蓝图实现。核心卖点是状态机驱动的 AI 系统和 Enhanced Input 的精细操控。</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/5">
          <h2 class="text-white text-xl font-bold mb-4">技术栈</h2>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-lg p-4"><span class="text-blue-400 text-sm">引擎</span><p class="text-white mt-1">Unreal Engine 5.7</p></div>
            <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-lg p-4"><span class="text-blue-400 text-sm">编程</span><p class="text-white mt-1">蓝图（纯蓝图，无 C++）</p></div>
            <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-lg p-4"><span class="text-blue-400 text-sm">输入</span><p class="text-white mt-1">Enhanced Input System</p></div>
            <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-lg p-4"><span class="text-blue-400 text-sm">AI</span><p class="text-white mt-1">StateTree 驱动</p></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/5">
          <h2 class="text-white text-xl font-bold mb-4">进度</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div>
              <div class="flex justify-between text-sm mb-1"><span class="text-white">阶段一 · 基础框架</span><span class="text-blue-400">⏳ 进行中</span></div>
              <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">角色移动、状态机、基础交互</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
